 for improved efficiency

- Introduced a singleton pattern for SessionManager to prevent duplicate initializations across multiple app instances, enhancing resource management.
- Updated LLMManager to lazily import the token budget module, ensuring that global averages are updated correctly without unnecessary overhead.
- Added thread safety to session creation in SessionManager, allowing for concurrent access without data corruption.
