From 3847cb310b5171ea838b0df5fa026705d2f5979a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: arterm-sedov <artem.sedov@comindware.com>
Date: Sun, 25 Jan 2026 02:05:23 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 08/29] Refactor UIManager and ChatTab for event-driven updates

- Enhanced UIManager to wire clear and stop events for dynamic UI updates, removing reliance on timer-based refresh for stats and progress.
- Updated ChatTab to utilize Gradio's native clear button, consolidating clear functionality and improving memory management.
- Improved event handling for UI updates after chat interactions, ensuring a more responsive user experience.
---
