 agent_ng/session_manager.py |  12 +++++
 agent_ng/tabs/chat_tab.py   | 101 +++++++++++++++++++++---------------
 agent_ng/ui_manager.py      |  63 ++++++++++++++--------
 4 files changed, 127 insertions(+), 62 deletions(-)

