Subject: [PATCH 09/29] Enhance message streaming and UI updates with language
 support

- Updated message streaming methods in NextGenApp and CmwAgent to include language parameter for improved internationalization (i18n).
- Added budget update event handling in NativeLangChainStreaming to refresh token budget display efficiently.
- Refactored UIManager to wire initialization completion updates, ensuring timely UI refreshes and improved user experience.
- Implemented hybrid approach for token budget updates, combining immediate event-driven updates with timer fallback for robustness.
