From 500f93a1803baa611dbd55cce4618ff940236740 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: arterm-sedov <arterm.sedov@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 20:13:43 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 13/29] fix(gradio): Gradio 6.13 queue setup and chat stop
 cancel wiring

QueueManager now records configured Blocks by instance id so the launched demo receives .queue() instead of being skipped after an ephemeral Blocks.

ChatTab: msg.stop must cancel the queued streaming dependency; submit_event stays the chain tail (stream.then(re-enable)) for UI manager .then() hooks.

Remove unsupported Textbox show_copy_button for Gradio 6.x.

Bump requirements floors to gradio>=6.13.0 and gradio_client>=2.5.0.
