From 0187e9413bad5c71bb200ea35390b746c5bc69e6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: arterm-sedov <arterm.sedov@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 23:40:08 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 14/29] fix(gradio6): cut post-stream stalls; tab bisect and
 deferred downloads

Defer Markdown/HTML export preparation until the user opens the Downloads tab unless CMW_UI_DOWNLOAD_PREP_AFTER_STREAM is set. HTML generation on the hot path stays behind CMW_UI_EXPORT_HTML_AFTER_TURN (default off).

Add CMW_UI_TABS, CMW_UI_TAB_LIMIT, CMW_UI_STACK_HOME_CHAT, and CMW_UI_DISABLE_AUTO_TIMERS for bisecting the Gradio 6 layout; extract build_ui() on tabs and wire optional stacked home+chat layout.

Document env toggles in AGENTS.md and cover allowlist parsing in tests.
