From 2b75d14d18e116a5bf7c3582c0f7545f9b44868b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: arterm-sedov <arterm.sedov@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 00:25:48 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 16/29] fix(gradio6): HTML export gate, Chat-first tabs, export
 text + debug timing

Reintroduce CMW_UI_EXPORT_HTML_AFTER_TURN (default off) so HTML generation stays opt-in when it stalls the UI.

Default tab order is Chat before Home unless CMW_UI_HOME_FIRST is set (mitigates Home-first freezes with many tabs). Restore Home TabItem render_children=True.

Downloads tab stacks Markdown then HTML download buttons. Add Gradio 6 multimodal content normalization for exports plus unit tests.

Add NDJSON tab-build timing (debug-392eaf.log) in UIManager for create_tab per module and full gr.Tabs duration.
