-- **HQ** — ``queue_manager.configure_queue``: branch + kwargs applied to ``demo.queue``.
-- **HL** — ``create_interface`` queue snapshot; ``main`` launch_enter (port / server).
-- **H11** — export path session id from ``session_manager`` (not ``DebugStreamer``).
