+- **Gradio UI bisect (dev only):** **`CMW_UI_*`** toggles for regressions or tuning—shell or local **`.env`**, not **`.env.example`**; contracts in **`agent_ng/agent_config.py`**. **Tabs:** **`CMW_UI_TABS`** beats **`CMW_UI_TAB_LIMIT`**; **`CMW_UI_STACK_HOME_CHAT`** stacks home+chat (no tab bar); **`CMW_UI_DISABLE_AUTO_TIMERS`** drops **`gr.Timer`** ticks. **`downloads`** must be built for Chat→downloads **`.then`**. **Exports:** **`CMW_UI_HOME_FIRST`** defaults **Home first**; **`0`**/**`false`**/**`no`**/**`off`** ⇒ Chat first. **`CMW_UI_EXPORT_HTML_AFTER_TURN`** and **`CMW_UI_DOWNLOAD_PREP_AFTER_STREAM`** default **off**. **`get_demo_with_language_detection()`** rebuilds cached **`demo`** when **`CMW_UI_TABS`**, **`CMW_UI_TAB_LIMIT`**, **`CMW_UI_STACK_HOME_CHAT`**, **`CMW_UI_DISABLE_AUTO_TIMERS`**, or **`CMW_UI_HOME_FIRST`** change (**`_ui_experiment_signature`**); other **`CMW_UI_*`** ⇒ **restart**.
 
